{"article_id":"ptosvgZfwgmgpYev","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"We already know","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"that","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"Michael Flynn believes","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"seeking immunity from prosecution","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"in return for testifying in an investigation","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"means `` you have probably committed a crime . ''","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"But","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"now that Flynn , President Trump 's first , brief national security adviser , is reportedly seeking immunity himself","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"to talk with the FBI and House and Senate intelligence committees","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"investigating Trump 's ties to Russia ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"what does that mean for Flynn","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"- and for Trump ?","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"It does n't look great for Flynn ,","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"legal experts say ,","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"but it is n't necessarily terrible for Trump .","depth":4},{"id":15,"text":"Essentially , everybody needs to calm down","depth":4},{"id":16,"text":"and let the legal dance play out .","depth":4},{"id":17,"text":"First , though Flynn `` certainly has a story","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"to tell ,","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"and he very much wants to tell it ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"should the circumstances permit , ''","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"his lawyer , Robert Kelner , said Thursday night ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"he has so far `` found no takers , ''","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"The Wall Street Journal reports .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"Flynn 's suggested deal `` has been met with initial skepticism , ''","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"The Washington Post says .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Investigators are `` unwilling to broker a deal , ''","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"The New York Times explains ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"`` until they are further along in their inquiries","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"and they better understand what information Mr. Flynn might offer as part of a deal . ''","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"There are basically two types of immunity","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"Flynn could get .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"Congress can only offer him `` testimonial '' or `` use '' immunity ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"which would prevent his testimony from being used against him in any prosecution .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"The Justice Department can grant Flynn full or `` transactional '' immunity for any potential crimes","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"committed .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"Congress does n't usually grant immunity","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"without a green light from the Justice Department ,","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"because even testimonial immunity would make it very difficult to prosecute Flynn","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"- a situation","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"that arose in the Iran-Contra case ,","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"where the immunity","depth":15},{"id":42,"text":"Congress granted Oliver North","depth":15},{"id":43,"text":"was used","depth":15},{"id":44,"text":"to overturn his later conviction .","depth":15},{"id":45,"text":"The Senate clearly does not `` want to screw up a possible prosecution , ''","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"former federal prosecutor Peter Zeidenberg tells The Washington Post .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"At the same time , as in the North investigation , the Senate could decide","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"`` there may be things more important","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"than getting a prosecution of Flynn , ''","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"like learning the scope of the Trump team 's ties to Russian officials .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"`` That is a compelling and urgent need , ''","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"he adds .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"`` A prosecution of Flynn could take several years .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"I would n't want them to wait that long","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"to find out what Flynn knows . ''","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"Jeffrey Toobin was associate counsel to the Iran-Contra and Oliver North prosecutor , Edward Walsh ,","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"and he explained on CNN Thursday night","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"how Congress and the Justice Department will feel pressure","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"to coordinate on the Flynn case :","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"Toobin on Flynn immunity discussion :","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"It means Flynn is taking the fifth .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"He 's refusing to testify","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"without immunity .","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"https : //t.co/ODKPkZRZum","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"- Anderson Cooper 360°","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"( @ AC360 )","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"March 31 , 2017","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"Toobin also touched on the `` proffer '' stage of most immunity negotiations .","depth":4},{"id":69,"text":"Alex Whiting , a former federal and International Criminal Court prosecutor","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"who now teaches at Harvard ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"explains the proffer process at Just Security","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"- and why it suggests","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"the loud overture from Flynn 's lawyer is `` not a serious offer ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"and it suggests","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"he has nothing to say","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"( or is not willing to say anything","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"that would incriminate others ) '' :","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"As an experienced lawyer , Kelner will know","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"that the Justice Department would never grant immunity for testimony on these terms .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"Prosecutors would first require","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"that Flynn submit to what 's called a proffer session","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"in which Flynn would agree to tell everything","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"he knows","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"in exchange for the prosecutors agreeing not to use his statement against him .","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"Only after the prosecutors heard what Flynn could offer in terms of evidence against others ,","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"and had an opportunity","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"to assess his credibility ,","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"would they be willing to discuss any grants of immunity or a cooperation deal ....","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"If he had something good ,","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"Flynn and his lawyer would approach the prosecutors quietly ,","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"go through the proffer process in confidence ,","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"and reach a deal .","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"Why ?","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"Because prosecutors have an interest","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"in keeping their investigation secret ,","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"and Flynn 's lawyer knows that .","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"The last thing","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"Flynn 's lawyer would do","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"if he thought","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"he had the goods","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"would be to go public ,","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"because that would potentially compromise the criminal inquiry","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"and would certainly irritate the prosecutors , the very people","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"Flynn 's lawyer would be trying to win over .","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"[ Whiting , Just Security ]","depth":5},{"id":106,"text":"Flynn does appear to be vulnerable to prosecution on fronts other than Russian election meddling ,","depth":4},{"id":107,"text":"as T. R. Ramachandran argues in a curated series of tweets .","depth":4},{"id":108,"text":"But Harvard national security expert Juliette Kayyem","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"-","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"who created a stir last week","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"when she suggested","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"Flynn was about to start cooperating with the FBI -","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"says","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"it really is n't clear what Flynn is willing to proffer : .","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"@ juliettekayyem signaled days ago","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"that Flynn may seek immunity for testimony :","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"'we were heading to this moment '","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"https : //t.co/SjWzn4kpFz","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"- Anderson Cooper 360°","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"( @ AC360 )","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"March 31 , 2017","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"`` The idea","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"that this goes directly to the Oval Office ,","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"we 're not there yet","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"- these cases take a long time , ''","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"Kayyem said .","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"`` But certainly , this is basically horrible news for the White House at this stage . ''","depth":6},{"id":128,"text":"`` No sane lawyer lets his client proffer , ''","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"California trial attorney Robert Barnes tells Legal Newz ,","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"`` because a proffer can be used against you","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"if you ever choose to testify in your own defense ,","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"except in special cases","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"where you have complete confidence","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"your client has little risk . ''","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"That does n't fit Flynn ,","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"so he 's actually signaling","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"that `` he is going to take the fifth on everything , ''","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"Barnes adds ,","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"unless he 's granted `` carte blanche immunity ,","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"which","depth":15},{"id":141,"text":"he and his lawyer know","depth":15},{"id":142,"text":"the government is never going to give","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"( because it requires specialized approvals","depth":14},{"id":144,"text":"it wo n't get ) .","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"What looks like a hostile signal to Trump is actually a self-defense signal","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"that Flynn wo n't be saying anything at all . ''","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"Mark Zaid , a lawyer","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"who specializes in national security cases ,","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"agrees","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"that , `` at this early stage , I would suggest","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"the request for immunity is more about skillful lawyering than anything else . ''","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"Still ,","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"he cautions at Legal Newz ,","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"`` the Trump administration better hope","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"that 's all it is . ''","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"Since Flynn is the one","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"`` putting out the sign 'info for immunity , ' ''","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"adds former federal prosecutor Henry E. Hockeimer ,","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"`` this may be more about a guy","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"simply trying to avoid prosecution .","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"If the government is n't coming to him","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"it may be because they already know what he would say . ''","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"Whiting says","depth":8},{"id":164,"text":"it looks to him like `` Flynn 's lawyer is really targeting Congress ''","depth":9},{"id":165,"text":"and `` hoping","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"that one of the Congressional committees will take the bait","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"and grant him immunity in exchange for his testimony ''","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"so the feds wo n't be able to touch him .","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"But using the Oliver North tactic `` is not going to work '' for Flynn ,","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"he predicts ,","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"and Congress has already signaled","depth":9},{"id":172,"text":"that it is n't interested .","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"In the end ,","depth":10},{"id":174,"text":"Whiting says ,","depth":10},{"id":175,"text":"`` the ploy feels desperate ,","depth":9},{"id":176,"text":"indicating","depth":9},{"id":177,"text":"that Flynn may not have much to offer .","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"And the very fact","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"that Flynn 's lawyer is making a play for immunity at this stage","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"suggests","depth":10},{"id":181,"text":"that he has some fear","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"that his client faces real criminal exposure . ''","depth":10},{"id":183,"text":"That 's bad for Flynn ,","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"but a possible silver lining for a White House","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"that can use all the good news","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"it can muster .","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":373,"left":242,"right":372,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":242,"left":201,"right":241,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":201,"left":198,"right":200,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":192,"right":197,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":192,"left":0,"right":191,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":1,"right":190,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":190,"left":2,"right":189,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":189,"left":188,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":188,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":195,"right":196,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":195,"left":6,"right":194,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":194,"left":7,"right":193,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":193,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":10,"